parameters:
Maid: Oh no, it's a mess! I have to
clean up!

Zerachiel: Huh? What are you talking
about??

Maid: I-I apologize! You just looked so
much like the madam...!!

Maid: But, I was surprised. You really
look so similar...

Maid: Master, you raised my salary! I
will work even harder than before!

Maid: Maybe I should go back to my
hometown too... I'm worried about my
family.

Maid: I'm quitting my job as a maid this
month!

Maid: I want to go back to my hometown
and put my parents' minds at ease, you
know!

Maid: Being naked, isn't it wonderful!
The mistress was also doing it!!

The maid: The master and mistress had a
very good relationship.

Maid: However, the mistress passed away
due to an incurable illness...

Maid: Master, I have started eating
properly. It's all thanks to you!

Maid: Master, thanks to you protecting
us, we are safe.

Maid: I intend to continue being a maid.
After all, I owe it to my master.

Maid: Hehe, the mistress used to undress
like that too. It brings back memories.
